snippet.title: Reouija Sleepover | Full Game + All Endings | What messing with a ouija with ur boy be like
snippet.description:
Reouija Sleepover, the remake, is a horror RPG maker game about Aiden and Dan who are just supposed to have netflix and chill (:3) in the former's apartment. Well, Aiden has to clean up and throw the trash but when he did, there's a ouija board in the bin! What could go wrong, right? What could?!

SP: I am telling you, everything could go wrong!!
SP1: I love all the cute cut scenes hehehehehe.
SP2: You know what, I just found online a lovely couple - a gay and a trans (female to male). They looked so adorable together and when asked what if they'd have a child, the other pair (gay) answered that he'd like a girl so he'd have someone to style and dress up with. Unfortunately, they broke up!!! (T^T) MY HEART COULDN'T TAKE IT!

All the endings:
22:58 - Bad Ending 1
50:37 - Bad Ending 2
1:03:52 - Bad Ending 3
1:13:33 - Alternative Ending (Main Ending)
1:27:37 - True Ending (Main Ending)

Hatoge also made these awesome games. Check them out!
Misfiction: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OFAuOco1GMU
Sofia?: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Hzqtug4RZVs
Mistrick: https://youtu.be/watch?v=gFGeUK9hY3Q

The walkthrough for all the endings is available when you download the game and on the game's page.
